g (see what works in your niche) Market benchmarking (are you above/below industry standards?) LTV prediction (focus on high-value customer acquisition) Immediate Setup Actions (Day 2-3): ✅ Install Shopify integration ✅ Connect ad platforms ✅ Set up competitor tracking (5-10 competitors) ✅ Enable Henri AI advisor ✅ Review initial market audit Expected Outputs Week 1: Competitive intelligence report Your position vs. market benchmarks LTV predictions by traffic source Pricing optimization recommendations 💰 Total Core Investment: $228/month TIER 2: Enhancement Layer (Add Week 2-3 if budget allows) If Attribution is Critical: Add Bily ($66/mo) Deploy If: You're spending $5k+/month on Meta/TikTok ads iOS 14.5+ has significantly reduced your attribution accuracy You need more accurate ROAS data for scaling decisions What It Fixes: Server-side event tracking (bypasses browser blockers) More accurate conversion attribution Better data for Triple Whale & Lebesgue to analyze ⚠️ Consideration: Triple Whale has its own pixel. Test if Bily provides measurable improvement before committing long-term. Skip Growify Because: 80% feature overlap with Triple Whale Triple Whale has superior AI agents Growify's strength (attribution) is already covered Budget better spent elsewhere during holiday rush 📋 Week-by-Week Holiday Season Implementation SOP WEEK 1 (November 2-8, 2025): Foundation Setup Day\tTool\tAction Steps\tExpected Input\tExpected Output\tTime Required Day 1\tTriple Whale\t1. Install from Shopify App Store 2. Connect Shopify store 3. Install Triple Whale Pixel 4. Connect bank account/Stripe\tStore URL, admin access, payment method\tDashboard populated with 30-day historical data\t1-2 hours Day 2\tTriple Whale\t1. Connect Meta Ads Manager 2. Connect Google Ads 3. Connect TikTok Ads (if applicable) 4. Connect email platform (Klaviyo)\tAd account IDs, API access tokens\tReal-time ad performance tracking active\t2-3 hours Day 3\tTriple Whale\t1. Activate Creative Analysis Agen