les Phase\tStrategy\tExpected Results Cyber Monday (Dec 2)\t• Repeat Black Friday playbook with fresh creative angles • Target Black Friday browsers who didn't buy • Bundle deals emphasized • Free shipping threshold\tRevenue target: 75-90% of Black Friday sales December 3-7\t• Shift from \"sale urgency\" to \"gift giving\" • Product bundling focus increases • Maintain profitable ROAS (3x+) • Reduce discount depth gradually\tMaintain elevated revenue at sustainable profit margins 🎁 Product Bundling Strategy (Since None of These Tools Auto-Create Bundles) Step-by-Step Bundle Creation Process Step\tAction\tData Source\tExpected Input\tExpected Output 1. Identify Opportunities\tRun \"Frequently Bought Together\" analysis\tTriple Whale Product Agent\t90 days of order data\tTop 20 product pairs with >25% co-purchase rate 2. Calculate Margins\tCalculate profitability of bundles\tShopify product costs + shipping\tCOGS, shipping costs, individual prices\tBundle margin analysis spreadsheet 3. Create Bundles\tBuild bundles in Shopify\tN/A\tProduct combinations, bundle pricing (10-20% discount)\t5-10 bundle SKUs created in Shopify 4. Test & Promote\tA/B test bundle visibility\tTriple Whale + Lebesgue\tBundle placement (product page vs. cart)\tBundle sales data, AOV impact 5. Monitor & Optimize\tTrack bundle performance\tTriple Whale Product Agent\tWeekly bundle sales metrics\tContinue top 3 bundles, pause bottom 2, create 2 new tests Recommended Bundles for Holiday 2025: \"Complete Gift Set\" - Your top 3 bestselling products at 15% off \"Starter Kit\" - Entry-level product + essential add-ons at 10% off \"Premium Experience\" - Top-tier product + premium accessories at 20% off \"Stocking Stuffers\" - 3-5 small items at 25% off \"Cyber Week Special\" - Time-limited bundle (Dec 1-7 only) ⚠️ Critical Success Factors & Common Pitfalls to Avoid ✅ DO THIS: Set Clear Baselines (Week 1): Record your current ROAS, CPA, conversion rate, AOV BEFORE implementing changes Trust the AI Agents: Triple Whale's agents are trained on billions in ad spend - follow their recommendations Daily Monitoring During Peak: Black Friday/Cyber Monday require multiple daily check-ins Mobile App Setup: Install Triple Whale mobile app for on-the-go monitoring Backup Plan: Have 3-5 proven backup creatives ready if primary ads fatigue Inventory Buffer: Order 2.5-3x normal inventory for top 20 products ❌ DON'T DO THIS: Don't Ignore Agent Alerts: When Moby Agent says \"Pause this ad,\" do it within 1-2 hours max Don't Over-Discount: Lebesgue will show you market benchmarks - don't race to bottom on pricing Don't Set & Forget: Even with AI agents, human oversight is critical during holiday season Don't Panic Over Daily Fluctuations: Look at 3-day rolling averages, not single-day performance Don't Ignore Stockouts: Triple Whale will alert you - reorder immediately or pause ads for that product Don't Add Too Many Tools: Stick with 2-tool stack (Triple Whale + Lebesgue) - more creates confusion 📊 Expected ROI & Timeline Metric\tBefore Tools\tWeek 2\tWeek 4\tBlack Friday Week\tDecember Average ROAS\t2.8x\t3.2x (+14%)\t3.8x (+36%)\t4.5x (+61%)\t3.9x (+39%) CPA\t$45\t$41 (-9%)\t$36 (-20%)\t$32 (-29%)\t$37 (-18%) Conversion Rate\t2.1%\t2.3% (+10%)\t2.6% (+24%)\t3.4% (+62%)\t2.7% (+29%) AOV\t$82\t$85 (+4%)\t$91 (+11%)\t$103 (+26%)\t$94 (+15%) Monthly Revenue\t$50,000\t$57,500\t$68,000\t$85,000 (weekly)\t$73,000 Total Investment: $228/month × 2 months = $456 Expected Additional Revenue: $50,000 (November + December combined) Net Profit Increase (at 25% margin): ~$12,500 ROI: 2,640% over 60 days 🚀 Final Recommendation: Start TODAY This Weekend (November 2-3): ✅ Install Triple Whale - Growth Plan ($149/mo) ✅ Install Lebesgue - Ultimate Plan ($79/mo) ✅ Connect all data sources ✅ Review initial dashboards By Wednesday November 6: Complete Week 1 SOP Have first optimization recommendations Begin implementing changes Why Rush? Black Friday is only 22 days away (November 28, 2025) Tools nee